    "We build a VQE algorithm where, taking inspiration from ref.",
    "49, we use a native photonic ansatz.",
    "We perform multiclass classification on the well-known IRIS dataset 50.",
    "To the best of our knowledge, this is the first experimental implementation of a variational quantum classifier with single photons; we refer to ref.",
    "51 for a realization on a superconducting platform and to ref."
